      "content": "idk i'm just worried because it's a really specific kind of pain. like it feels like a stabbing sensation. do u really think a walk and some water will fix it? i feel like if it was an emergency i'd know, right? it's probably just the caffeine and the flight stress. u sure it's not anything serious?",
